                               @{fg highlight}DISTRIBUTION@{fg text}
                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~

 Any commercial use of this material is ILLEGAL, however files contained
 in this archive can be copied freely without any fee (support cost only),
 but take care: this archive can be placed only on AmiNet and on "Amiga
 based" CD-ROMs (as well as on floppy disks).

 The files contained in the archive IntelOut.lha
 -----------------------------------------------
 The_Intel_Outside.med           Music module (MED)
 The_Intel_Outside_Cover.ilbm    Pseudo-cover of the track
 The_Intel_Outside.guide         This AmigaGuide file
 The_Intel_Outside.ReadMe        A short ReadMe text file
 OctaMED_Player_V5.10            The player you need
 OctaMED_Player.guide            The player guide
 OctaPlayer.library              The library for the player
 some .info files                Icons (as you know :)

 Note: the pseudo-cover is 640x512x7 video overscan (128 colors).
@endnode

