 People are waiting for a new operating system,
 PC people think you'll never beat 'em.
 Oh no no no no I, I don't want to follow the PC side,
 oh no no no no I, I can't stop dreaming with Amiga in the sky.
 Forever and ever, and ever and ever I'll live like Marty Mc Fly...
 with the Intel Outside, the system we like,
 the Intel Outsiiide.
 It's the Intel Outside, the system we have,
 the Intel Outsiiide,
 yeaaahhh...
